   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="bibliography" subtype="edition">
            <ab>Translated in <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:finot-1915c"/>: <biblScope>112</biblScope></bibl>; whence <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:majumdar-1927"/>: <biblScope>28</biblScope></bibl> and <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:golzio-2004"/>: <biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>. The present edition and translation after <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:ECIC-III"/>: <biblScope>463-464</biblScope></bibl>.</ab>
         </div>        
         <div type="edition" xml:lang="x-oldcam-Latn-CI" xml:space="preserve" rend="break-none">
            <div type="textpart" n="1">
               <head xml:lang="en">C. 127.1</head>
            <ab>
            <lb n="1"/> namaś śivāya
            <lb n="2"/> śrīprakāśadharmmā jaya<unclear>ti</unclear>
            </ab>
            </div>
         </div>         
         <div type="apparatus">
            <head xml:lang="en">C. 127.1</head>
            <p>
               <app loc="2">
                  <lem>jaya<unclear>ti</unclear></lem>
                  <rdg resp="Finot">jayadā<supplied reason="lost">naṃ</supplied></rdg>
                  <note>This reading was repeated, without square brackets and introducing a new variation (<foreign>prakāśavarmmā</foreign>), in <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:schweyer-2009a"/>: <biblScope>35, note 60</biblScope></bibl>.</note>
               </app>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="edition" xml:lang="x-oldcam-Latn-CI" xml:space="preserve" rend="break-none">
            <div type="textpart" n="2">
               <head xml:lang="en">C. 127.2</head>
            <ab>
            <lb n="1"/> śrīcampeśvara
            </ab>
            </div>
         </div>       
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <head xml:lang="en">C. 127.1</head> <!-- AL: I removed <div type="textpart"> to try to get a left aligned head (as it was in C. 3. 2)-->
            <p>Homage to Śiva. Śrī Prakāśadharmmā triumphs!</p>
            <head xml:lang="en">C. 127.2</head>
            <p>Lord of Campā.</p>
            </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
               <head xml:lang="fr">C. 127.1</head>
            <p>Hommage à Śiva. Śrī Prakāśadharmmā triomphe!</p>
               <head xml:lang="fr">C. 127.2</head>
               <p>Seigneur du Campā.</p>
         </div>
